title: $1.5 billion in funding for university research (Department of Education and Training - Australian Government) ...
text: ( Source : Department of Education and Training - Australian Government ) More than $1.5 billion will be available over four years to support Australia's world-class university researchers following the introduction of new laws into Parliament
